data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":265,"item_id":"msg_c3422573eac6105d00693a2dc032a88190b9b3ed60500604d3","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso's Smart Eyewear, specifically SmartView Glasses, includes a variety of features designed to enhance user experience:\n\n### Features\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: The glasses provide a digital overlay on real-world environments, offering immersive experiences.\n\n2. **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: This feature allows for hands-free operation using voice commands, making it highly user-friendly.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Enables users to capture high-quality video along with spatial audio, perfect for creating rich multimedia content.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Protects your eyes from harmful UV rays and reduces blue light exposure, which is beneficial for extended use.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Designed for convenience, the glasses support wireless charging and offer a long battery life.\n\n### Additional Details\n\n- **User Guide**: Includes sections on introduction, product overview, sizing, fit adjustments, care and maintenance, safety tips, and troubleshooting.\n- **Warranty**: Comes with a two-year limited warranty covering electronic components.\n- **Return Policy**: Offers a 30-day return policy without any questions asked.\n\nThese features underscore the advanced technology and thoughtful design behind Contoso's Smart Eyewear.","logprobs":[]}

